# Ref

GDB Remote Protocol:
* Apple: https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/DeveloperTools/gdb/gdb/gdb_33.html
* General query packets: https://sourceware.org/gdb/current/onlinedocs/gdb.html/General-Query-Packets.html
* LLDB: https://lldb.llvm.org/resources/lldbplatformpackets.html


# Run

```
cccc main.cpp
lldb
(lldb) log enable gdb-remote packets -T
(lldb) file a.out
(lldb) b main
(lldb) r
```

The following log will be printed.
